Problem Statement

You are building a Cross-Platform UI Toolkit.
Your application should support multiple operating systems:
Windows
macOS

Each operating system provides its own UI components:
Button
Checkbox

Requirement
UI components must be platform-specific
Components from the same platform must be used together
Client code should not depend on concrete classes
Switching platform should be easy (Windows â†’ macOS)

What this problem tests
Understanding of family of related objects
Why Factory alone is not enough
How Abstract Factory enforces consistency

Hint
Think in terms of:
Button interface
Checkbox interface
UIFactory abstract factory
WindowsUIFactory, MacUIFactory

